	test_fonts-$_testfonts.tar.gz::https://chromium-fonts.storage.googleapis.com/$_testfonts
	copium-$_copium_tag.tar.gz::https://codeberg.org/selfisekai/copium/archive/$_copium_tag.tar.gz
